snippet.title: Bleeding Edge Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Team Up. Cause Chaos. https://xbx.lv/33GymhW

Bleeding Edge is a 4v4 team fighter coming March 24 2020 on Xbox One, Windows 10, and Steam. Pre-order or play with Xbox Game Pass between March 24-31 2020 to receive the Punk Pack!

#BleedingEdge
